What do you think that most normal people would be surprised to know

100
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:06,000
about the powerful and the rich individuals, world views,

101
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:09,000
the way that they hold themselves, what is and isn't true?

102
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:13,000
They feel powerless.

103
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:19,000
That's one of the craziest things is that very often you're at a table

104
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:25,000
of people of immeasurable wealth and they're talking about the rich

105
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,000
or the hyper-connected.

106
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:30,000
They don't see themselves in these terms.

107
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,000
Why?

108
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:34,000
I think there's different kinds of rich, to be honest.

109
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:42,000
I think that if, for example, you got rich from, let's say, arms manufacturing,

110
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:46,000
you've been entwined with government your whole life or agriculture,

111
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:53,000
something that's highly regulated that extraction oil and gas.

